1. *Dušice* su lekovite biljke koje se koriste u narodnoj medicini. (Thyme is a medicinal plant used in folk medicine.)
2. Čaj od *dušica* pomaže kod kašlja i prehlade. (Thyme tea helps with cough and cold.)
3. Ukoliko želite da jelo bude aromatično, dodajte malo *dušica*. (If you want the dish to be aromatic, add some thyme.)
4. *Dušice* su sastojak mnogih jela u mediteranskoj kuhinji. (Thyme is an ingredient in many Mediterranean dishes.)
5. Da bi se dobio intenzivniji ukus, *dušice* se dodaju na kraju kuvanja. (To get a more intense flavor, thyme is added at the end of cooking.)
6. Moja baka pravi fantastičan sos sa *dušicama*. (My grandmother makes a fantastic sauce with thyme.)
7. Ova piletina ima divan miris zahvaljujući *dušicama*. (This chicken has a wonderful smell thanks to the thyme.)
8. *Dušice* su jedna od najpopularnijih začinskih biljaka u svetu. (Thyme is one of the most popular herbs in the world.)
9. Da bi se dobila savršena kombinacija ukusa, koristi se mešavina *dušica* i ruzmarina. (To achieve the perfect combination of flavors, a mixture of thyme and rosemary is used.)
10. *Dušice* se mogu koristiti i u svežem i u sušenom obliku. (Thyme can be used in fresh and dried form.)